Package: srcpd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: SRCP 0.8.2 server daemon
 srcpd is a Simple Railroad Command Protocol server (SRCP Version 0.8.2)
 transmitting commands from and to SRCP clients or connected digital
 model railway control units.
 srcpd can act as central contol unit and directly generate and feed
 Motorola or DCC signals to the booster of the digital model railway
 layout or as well transmit commands to other control units connected to
 the serial interface.
